---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About LBS AI Lab — Strategic Direction & Mission" 
  description="Learn about the strategic vision of LBS AI Lab, how we help students become AI-native leaders, and our alignment with the Data Science & AI Initiative at London Business School."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="about-hero" aria-label="About Introduction">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge badge-red" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">About LBS AI Lab</span>
      <h1 class="about-headline">AI fluency through real product building.</h1>
      <p class="about-subheadline">
        The Lab exists to help future leaders understand AI transformation from the inside: by building products, automating workflows, and testing ideas with real users.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Editorial Thesis Section -->
  <section class="thesis-section" aria-label="Our Thesis">
    <div class="container asymmetrical-grid">
      <div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Why we build</h2>
        <p class="thesis-lead">
          AI is changing how organisations make decisions, serve customers, operate teams, and create new ventures. Leaders who only understand AI conceptually will be at a disadvantage.
        </p>
        <p>
          The next generation of leaders needs practical fluency: the ability to prototype, evaluate, and deploy AI-enabled systems responsibly. It is not enough to talk about AI or attend guest panels. Real fluency requires opening a terminal, configuring APIs, prompting models, structuring data, and iterating on interface design.
        </p>
        <p>
          LBS AI Lab provides that environment. By bringing together ambitious LBS students with technical and product mentors, we translate abstract business opportunities into functional prototypes within a compressed, execution-focused timeline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="thesis-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-quote-box">
          <blockquote class="sidebar-quote">
            "Future leaders need direct experience building with AI, not just conceptual literacy."
          </blockquote>
          <cite class="sidebar-cite">— LBS AI Lab Manifesto</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Differentiators Section -->
  <section class="diff-section" aria-label="What Makes Us Different">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Strategic Position</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">What makes us different</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Most AI student initiatives focus on networking, tutorials, or brief hackathons. LBS AI Lab takes a different approach:
      </p>

      <div class="diff-grid">
        <div class="diff-card">
          <h3 class="diff-card-title">It is strictly hands-on</h3>
          <p class="diff-card-text">
            We measure progress in shipped code, live URLs, and real database integrations. If you cannot interact with it in a browser, it is not a finished Lab project.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <h3 class="diff-card-title">It is venture-oriented</h3>
          <p class="diff-card-text">
            Teams structure their projects like serious product teams. We focus on real problems, clear customer personas, functional APIs, and user onboarding.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <h3 class="diff-card-title">Student-led, institutionally aligned</h3>
          <p class="diff-card-text">
            The lab is run by LBS builders for LBS builders. We align directly with the high standards, ethics, and leadership principles of London Business School.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card">
          <h3 class="diff-card-title">Building as a leadership skill</h3>
          <p class="diff-card-text">
            We do not expect every participant to become a software engineer. We expect them to become executives who can direct technical teams because they've built systems themselves.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Methodology Section -->
  <section class="methodology-section" aria-label="Our Methodology">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">The Program</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">How the Lab works</h2>
      
      <div class="method-steps">
        <div class="method-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">01</span>
            <h3 class="step-title">Form & Align</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="step-text">
            Students propose ideas or apply to join existing project briefs. We structure balanced teams combining MBA operators, product designers, and technical builders.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="method-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">02</span>
            <h3 class="step-title">Focus & Scope</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="step-text">
            Teams refine their scope under the guidance of technical and product mentors. We strip away complexity to define a highly specific core MVP that can be built in weeks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="method-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">03</span>
            <h3 class="step-title">Build & Iterate</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="step-text">
            Teams build prototypes using modern serverless stacks, database models, and LLM integrations. We review progress weekly, assessing live builds at every checkpoint.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="method-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">04</span>
            <h3 class="step-title">Demo & Deploy</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="step-text">
            At the end of the cohort, teams ship their live products to public URLs, presenting their builds to LBS students, faculty, recruiters, and technical founders.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Parent Initiative Section -->
  <section class="alignment-section" id="dsai-alignment" aria-label="Institutional Alignment">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="align-box-full">
        <span class="badge badge-red" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Institutional Umbrella</span>
        <h2 class="align-title">Alignment with the Data Science & AI Initiative</h2>
        <div class="align-body">
          <p>
            LBS AI Lab operates under the Data Science & AI Initiative (DSAI) at London Business School, connecting student product building with the School's broader focus on responsible and strategic AI adoption.
          </p>
          <p>
            The DSAI Initiative turns insight into action, guiding responsible and strategic adoption of AI across business and society. LBS AI Lab extends that mission into hands-on product building for students, giving future leaders the practical capability to implement the playbooks and frameworks researched by the Initiative.
          </p>
          <div class="align-links">
            <a href="https://www.london.edu/faculty-and-research/data-science-and-ai-initiative" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Visit DSAI Platform</a>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="border-color: white; color: white;">Contact Initiative Team</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* About Page Specific Styles */
  .about-hero {
    background-color: var(--color-lbs-blue);
    padding-top: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-bottom: 6px solid var(--color-lbs-red);
  }

  .about-headline {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.6rem);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .about-subheadline {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    max-width: 800px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Thesis section styling */
  .thesis-section {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding-top: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .thesis-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-lbs-blue);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .thesis-sidebar {
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .sidebar-quote-box {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-lbs-red);
    padding-left: 24px;
    background-color: var(--color-cloud);
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .sidebar-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-lbs-blue);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .sidebar-cite {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  /* Differentiators styling */
  .diff-section {
    background-color: var(--color-warm-white);
    padding-top: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-lbs-red);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    color: var(--color-lbs-blue);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .diff-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .diff-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .diff-card {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 40px;
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .diff-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-lbs-blue);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }

  .diff-card-title {
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    color: var(--color-lbs-blue);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .diff-card-text {
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Methodology styling */
  .methodology-section {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding-top: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .method-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .method-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .method-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .method-step {
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    padding-top: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .method-step:hover {
    border-top-color: var(--color-lbs-red);
  }

  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-lbs-red);
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    color: var(--color-lbs-blue);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .step-text {
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Alignment styling */
  .alignment-section {
    background-color: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding-top: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
  }

  .align-box-full {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-lbs-red);
    padding-left: clamp(20px, 4vw, 40px);
  }

  .align-title {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .align-body p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 75ch;
  }

  .align-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .align-links .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--color-lbs-red);
    color: var(--color-lbs-red);
  }
</style>
